{"title":"WWDC live: Everything Apple announced in its jam-packed keynote","link":"https://www.macworld.com/article/2361079/wwdc-2024-keynote-live-blog-ios-18-macos-15-watchos-11.html","date":1718056974000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.macworld.com\">Macworld</a></p>\n\n<div>\n<section><div></div></section>\n\n\n\n<p>It’s time for the most impactful keynote Apple will deliver all year: <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/678333/wwdc-ios-macos-watchos-hardware-keynote.html\">WWDC</a>, when the company unveils the new direction it will take its devices. Today Apple unveiled <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/2221069/ios-18-ai-release-date-features-compatibility-beta.html\">iOS 18</a> and iPadOS 18, <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/2265062/macos-15-release-name-compatibility-features.html\">macOS 15</a>, and watchOS 11, along with updates to tvOS, AirPods, and visionOS, all coming this fall. It’s a big day.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>So if you’re as excited as we are, you’re tracking all of the latest news with our full coverage and live blog or just rewatch the keynote to relive it all over again.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>WWDC 2024: Everything Apple announced</h2>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/2362001/ios-18-new-features-apple-intelligence-home-screen-control-center-mail-messages.html\">iOS 18:</a> Customizable Home screen, Apple Intelligence, redesigned Photos</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/2362395/ipados-18-calculator-math-notes-apple-pencil-handwriting-equations.html\">iPadOS 18:</a> New Calculator app with hand-written Math Notes</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/2362011/watchos-11-watch-faces-fitness-vitals-translate.html\">watchOS 11:</a> New health and fitness features and apps, redesigned Photos face</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/2362235/macos-sequoia-introduces-iphone-mirroring-tiled-interface-and-ai-features.html\">macOS 15:</a> iPhone mirroring, tiled app layout, updated apps</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/2362200/visionos-2-photos-mac-virtual-display-home-screen-gestures.html\">visionOS 2:</a> Spatial photo creation, Mac virtual display enhancements</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>WWDC 2024: Live blog</h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>12:55pm ET:</strong> Apple’s stream is live with a Siri-colored ray of light tracing the edges of various objects.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>12:58pm:</strong> the YouTube stream (below) is also live.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1pm:</strong> The keynote is starting, revealing an image of a glowing Apple logo.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1pm:</strong> “It’s Showtime!” The opening skit involves Phil Schiller flying a plans with Craig Federighi and Apple execs jumping out of a plane!</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1:02pm:</strong> Tim Cook is opening the show with a segment on top of Apple Park. “Today we’re going to have some incredible updates to our platforms.”</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1:03pm:</strong> Apple TV+ is celebrating its 5th anniversary, “about to launch our most exciting lineup yet.” Severance is returning!</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1:05pm:</strong> “We’ll start with our OS announcements and dive into intelligence,” First up visionOS.</p>\n\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/visionos-2-features.png?w=1200\" alt=\"visionOS 2 features slide\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/visionos-2-features.png?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1920w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/visionos-2-features.png?resize=300%2C168&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/visionos-2-features.png?resize=768%2C432&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/visionos-2-features.png?resize=1200%2C675&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/visionos-2-features.png?resize=1536%2C864&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/visionos-2-features.png?resize=1240%2C697&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1240w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/visionos-2-features.png?resize=150%2C84&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"visionOS 2 features slide\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/visionos-2-features.png?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1920w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/visionos-2-features.png?resize=300%2C168&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/visionos-2-features.png?resize=768%2C432&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/visionos-2-features.png?resize=1200%2C675&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/visionos-2-features.png?resize=1536%2C864&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/visionos-2-features.png?resize=1240%2C697&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1240w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/visionos-2-features.png?resize=150%2C84&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>Apple</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"visionOS 2 features slide\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/visionos-2-features.png?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1920w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/visionos-2-features.png?resize=300%2C168&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/visionos-2-features.png?resize=768%2C432&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/visionos-2-features.png?resize=1200%2C675&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/visionos-2-features.png?resize=1536%2C864&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/visionos-2-features.png?resize=1240%2C697&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1240w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/visionos-2-features.png?resize=150%2C84&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>Apple</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div></div>\n\t\t</div></figure><p>Apple</p></div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1:08pm:</strong> visionOS 2 lets you create spatial photos from existing 2D photos using machine learning.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1:10pm:</strong> New gestures and higher resolution for Mac Virtual Display. Train support.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1:10pm: </strong>TableTopKit lets devs create games that lock to a surface.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1:12pm:</strong> Canon is offering a new spatial video lens for Vision Pro. Available this fall</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1:13pm:</strong> Apple Immersive Video available to creators. New immersive experiences on the way.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1:15pm:</strong> Vision Pro available in China, Japan, and Singapore on June 28. UK on July 12!</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1:15pm:</strong> It’s time for iOS 18!</p>\n\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/iOS-18-phones.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all\" alt=\"iOS 18 iPhone\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/iOS-18-phones.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/iOS-18-phones.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/iOS-18-phones.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/iOS-18-phones.jpg?resize=150%2C100&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"iOS 18 iPhone\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/iOS-18-phones.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/iOS-18-phones.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/iOS-18-phones.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/iOS-18-phones.jpg?resize=150%2C100&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>Apple</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"iOS 18 iPhone\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/iOS-18-phones.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/iOS-18-phones.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/iOS-18-phones.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/iOS-18-phones.jpg?resize=150%2C100&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>Apple</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div></div>\n\t\t</div></figure><p>Apple</p></div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1:16pm:</strong> Arrange apps anywhere you want on the screen. Dark-mode apps and customization sheet for tinting icons.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1:17pm:</strong> New controls in Control Center with groups. Controls gallery make it “more extensible than ever.” Third party controls too!</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1:19pm:</strong> You can now change the lock screen icons.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1:20pm:</strong> Lock an app—won’t launch without Face ID, Touch ID, or passcode. Hide an app in locked hidden apps folder. Users can decide which contents and devices apps can see.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1:21pm:</strong> Messages brings “all new ways to express yourself and stay connected.” Any emoji can be used as a tapback. Scheduled messages, new effects. SMS ans iMessages via satellite will let you text when off the grid (iPhone 14 and later). End-to-end encrypted.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1:23pm:</strong> Mail categories. Primary, transactions, updates, promotions. Sort mail and summarize messages in a digest view. Users can recategorize messages and easily archive and delete.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1:25pm:</strong> Topographic Maps. Tap to Cash in Wallet. Apple Pay online and a new design for event tickets. Insights and Search for Journal.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1:26pm:</strong> Game Mode comes to iPhone for an immersive experience.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1:27pm:</strong> Biggest redesign ever to the Photos app. Unified into a single view with months and years at the bottom and library at the top. Easily filter out screenshots. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1:29pm:</strong> Collections let you browse by topic with unrelated screenshots and images filtered out. People and Pets include groups. Trips view organizes travel by year and place. All customizable.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1:30pm:</strong> iOS 18: Option for larger icons on the home screen. Reminders and calendar integration.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1:31pm:</strong> AirPods!</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1:32pm:</strong> Shake your head yes or no to answer a call. Voice Isolation comes to AirPods Pro. Removes background noise while on a call.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1:33pm:</strong> Game mode with personalized spatial audio.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1:34pm: </strong>Apple TV: Insight. Swipe down on remote to see actors, characters, and songs in a movie or show. Enhanced dialog uses machine learning for better clarity. Subtitles automatically appear when muted or rewound. Snoopy screensaver!</p>\n\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/watchOS-11-new-features.png?w=1200\" alt=\"watchOS 11 new features\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/watchOS-11-new-features.png?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1920w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/watchOS-11-new-features.png?resize=300%2C168&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/watchOS-11-new-features.png?resize=768%2C432&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/watchOS-11-new-features.png?resize=1200%2C675&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/watchOS-11-new-features.png?resize=1536%2C864&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/watchOS-11-new-features.png?resize=1240%2C697&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1240w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/watchOS-11-new-features.png?resize=150%2C84&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"watchOS 11 new features\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/watchOS-11-new-features.png?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1920w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/watchOS-11-new-features.png?resize=300%2C168&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/watchOS-11-new-features.png?resize=768%2C432&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/watchOS-11-new-features.png?resize=1200%2C675&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/watchOS-11-new-features.png?resize=1536%2C864&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/watchOS-11-new-features.png?resize=1240%2C697&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1240w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/watchOS-11-new-features.png?resize=150%2C84&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>Apple</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"watchOS 11 new features\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/watchOS-11-new-features.png?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1920w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/watchOS-11-new-features.png?resize=300%2C168&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/watchOS-11-new-features.png?resize=768%2C432&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/watchOS-11-new-features.png?resize=1200%2C675&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/watchOS-11-new-features.png?resize=1536%2C864&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/watchOS-11-new-features.png?resize=1240%2C697&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1240w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/watchOS-11-new-features.png?resize=150%2C84&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>Apple</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div></div>\n\t\t</div></figure><p>Apple</p></div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1:36pm:</strong> watchOS 11: More new features to keep you active, healthy, and connected.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1:37pm:</strong> Training mode measure effort from “easy” to “all out” to adjust workouts.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1:38pm:</strong> Customize summary tab in Fitness app. Pause rings for a rest day, week, or more.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1:39pm:</strong> Vitals app: daily health status and important health metrics. Details on what’s changed and alerts when something may be concerning.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1:40pm:</strong> Cycle tracking can show gestational age during pregnancy and show heart rate.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1:40pm:</strong> Smart stacks automatically add new widgets when needed. Translation right on your wrist. Live activities coming to Apple Watch. Check In now on Apple Watch with support for late-night workouts. Redesigned Photos face.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1:43pm:</strong> iPadOS: Customizable home screen and control center like iOS. Floating tab bar morphs into side bar. Customizable. Easier to browse documents. Refined animations. All APIs for developers.</p>\n\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ipados_18_overview.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" alt=\"iPadOs 18 overview\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ipados_18_overview.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1920w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ipados_18_overview.jpg?resize=300%2C168&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ipados_18_overview.jpg?resize=768%2C432&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ipados_18_overview.jpg?resize=1200%2C675&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ipados_18_overview.jpg?resize=1536%2C864&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ipados_18_overview.jpg?resize=1240%2C697&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1240w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ipados_18_overview.jpg?resize=150%2C84&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"iPadOs 18 overview\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ipados_18_overview.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1920w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ipados_18_overview.jpg?resize=300%2C168&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ipados_18_overview.jpg?resize=768%2C432&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ipados_18_overview.jpg?resize=1200%2C675&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ipados_18_overview.jpg?resize=1536%2C864&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ipados_18_overview.jpg?resize=1240%2C697&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1240w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ipados_18_overview.jpg?resize=150%2C84&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>Apple</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"iPadOs 18 overview\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ipados_18_overview.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1920w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ipados_18_overview.jpg?resize=300%2C168&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ipados_18_overview.jpg?resize=768%2C432&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ipados_18_overview.jpg?resize=1200%2C675&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ipados_18_overview.jpg?resize=1536%2C864&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ipados_18_overview.jpg?resize=1240%2C697&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1240w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ipados_18_overview.jpg?resize=150%2C84&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>Apple</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div></div>\n\t\t</div></figure><p>Apple</p></div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1:45pm: </strong>SharePlay: Tap and draw on screen, remote control iPad or iPhone. Freeform adds Scenes to focus on specific sections.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1:47pm:</strong> CALCULATOR FOR iPAD. Write equations with Apple Pencil in Math Notes. Dynamic problem solving in handwriting. Works in Notes.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1:49pm: </strong>Smart script in Notes improves appearance of handwriting as you write to make it “smoother, straighter, and more legible.” Spell check, tap and hold to add space, scribble to erase.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1:52pm:</strong> macOS Sequoia! iPhone mirroring lets you control your iPhone from another room, use aps, interact with keyboard and trackpad, notifications from iPhone can be interacted with on the Mac. Audio comes through on Mac. iPhone stays locked.</p>\n\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/macos-sequoia-features.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" alt=\"macOS Sequoia features\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/macos-sequoia-features.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 2400w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/macos-sequoia-features.jpg?resize=300%2C168&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/macos-sequoia-features.jpg?resize=768%2C432&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/macos-sequoia-features.jpg?resize=1200%2C675&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/macos-sequoia-features.jpg?resize=1536%2C864&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/macos-sequoia-features.jpg?resize=2048%2C1152&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 2048w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/macos-sequoia-features.jpg?resize=1240%2C697&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1240w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/macos-sequoia-features.jpg?resize=150%2C84&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figu